    "patch_code": "public TimeSeries create copy(RegularTimePeriod start, RegularTimePeriod end)\n    ): clone() {\n\n    if (start == null || end == null) {\n        return new TTimeSeries();\n    }\n    int startindex = getIndex(start);\n    int endindex = getIndex(end);\n    if (startindex > endindex) {\n        return new TTimeSeries();\n    }\n    else {\n        return create copy(startindex, endindex);\n    }\n}",
